Title: Big Sir Candle
Body (HTML):
Rich, woody inlands over a misty coastline encapsulate the magic of Big Sur. This distinguished, smoky scent evokes fine leather and smooth tobacco with a dash of freshly cut bay leaves.

Notes of Tobacco, Leather & Bay Leaves

Title: Mojave Dessert Candle
Body (HTML):
Alluring desert nights marry earthy notes of cedarwood and patchouli with a hint of sweet jasmine. It’s a spicy mirage with warm wisps of amber noir.

 

Notes of Patchouli, Amber & Cedar

Title: Joshua Tea Candle
Body (HTML):
Sun-dried Earl Grey tea leaves fill the air with a tinge of ripened citrus and notes of bergamot. It’s a refreshing reprieve, like finding soothing shade in the hot desert sun.

Notes of Black Tea, Orange & Bergamot

Title: Nap Valley Candle
Body (HTML):
Delicate and airy linen sheets drying in a cool wine country breeze. Clean, and crisp, it’s reminiscent of a fresh open valley. 

Notes of Thyme, Violet & Seaberry

Title: Lady Bird Groove Candle
Body (HTML):
Lemony white magnolia, traces of fragrant gardenia, and night-blooming jasmine swirl together in this decadent floral trio. Inhale and imagine the wild flowers along the winding trails of Lady Bird Johnson Grove.

Notes of Jasmine, Magnolia & Gardenia

Title: Sacrameadow Candle
Body (HTML):
Fresh fields of morning dew dappled fern and delicate moss swirl together in this earthy delight. Evocative of Sacramento fields, breathe in and enjoy elegant undertones of lilac and moistened soil.

Notes of Moss, Fern & Lilac

Title: Half Moon Bae Candle
Body (HTML):
Sensuous spices of amber, cardamom, and clove evoke magical evenings cloaked in moonlight. Feel the Half Moon Bay breeze as it carries waves of salty goodness and hints of vanilla. 

Notes of Cardamom, Clove & Vanilla

Title: Santa Cruise Candle
Body (HTML):
Soothing notes of eucalyptus and vetiver remindful of where the ocean and the forest meet. Recall long, lazy afternoons along the shores of Santa Cruz where there’s nothing to do but breathe.

Notes of Eucalyptus, Vetiver & Sandalwood

Title: Joshua Tea Soap
Body (HTML):
Wrap yourself in nourishing moisture with our Goat’s Milk and Honey-based soap infused with Vitamin E. As you lather, sun-dried Earl Grey tea fills the air with a tinge of ripened citrus and notes of bergamot.

Like the candle, it’s a refreshing reprieve, like finding soothing shade in the hot desert sun.

Title: Lady Bird Groove Soap
Body (HTML): Rose Clay and Mango Butter combine to create an earthier, skin-softening version of our candle scent—that rinses clean while absorbing excess oil from your skin. Bathe and breathe in deliciously fragrant gardenia, and night-blooming jasmine.

Title: Mojave Dessert Soap
Body (HTML): A true treat for your skin, with activated charcoal to draw out excess oil and impurities, and Goats Milk, Vitamin E, and Honey to keep skin silky soft. Indulge your senses in the sweet smell of warm desert earth and cedar.

Title: Santa Cruise Soap
Body (HTML): Soothing, gentle Olive Oil and Vitamin E blend together with notes of eucalyptus and lavender evoking long afternoons on the shores of Santa Cruz where there’s nothing to do but breathe.

Title: Marina Del Ray Bath Salts
Body (HTML): Soak your senses in the restorative freshness of eucalyptus as you rejuvenate mind and body. It’s the feeling of sun, surf, and a day at the beach, without the sand in your suit.

Title: Hollywoods Bath Salts
Body (HTML): Nothing says calm like the soothing scent of lavender. Luxuriate in the fragrant aroma that’s reminiscent of a sublime flower-filled hike in Griffith park or Laurel Canyon.

Title: Candle Flights
Body (HTML):
Enjoy a tour of our favorite Golden State scents with our Candle Flight collections. Includes three 2oz. soy candles.

FRESH: Nap Valley, Joshua Tea, Sacrameadow.

FLORAL: Lady Bird Groove, Sacrameadow, Joshua Tea.

EARTH: Half Moon Bae, Santa Cruise, Mojave Dessert

MUSK: Mojave Dessert, Big Sir, Half Moon Bae.

Title: Journals
Body (HTML):
Our exquisite journals feature artwork from the women in our program. The journals are soft-covered with lined pages so you can write, draw, and doodle anything - - anytime, anywhere.

- Size 5 x 8
- Portrait oriented
- 80 Lined Pages

Body (HTML):
We’ve partnered with the masters at Paper Chase Press to offer exquisite notebooks featuring artwork from the women in our program. These journals feature 40 unlined pages and are available in sets of three.

- Each three pack features 2 notebooks with artwork + one solid color cover.

Title: Soap Bundle - 3.5oz 4pk Assortment
Body (HTML):
This 4pk features all of our hand-poured soaps, made in small batches by the women in our job training program.

Santa Cruise: Soothing, gentle Olive Oil and Vitamin E blend together with notes of eucalyptus and lavender evoking long afternoons on the shores of Santa Cruz where there’s nothing to do but breathe.

Mojave Dessert: A true treat for your skin, with activated charcoal to draw out excess oil and impurities, and Goats Milk, Vitamin E, and Honey to keep skin silky soft. Indulge your senses in the sweet smell of warm desert earth and cedar.

Joshua Tea: Our Goat’s Milk and Honey-based soap infused with Vitamin E. As you lather, sun-dried Earl Grey tea fills the air with a tinge of ripened citrus and notes of bergamot.

Lady Bird Groove: Rose Clay and Mango Butter combine to create an earthier, skin-softening version of our candle scent - that rinses clean while absorbing excess oil from your skin. Bathe and breathe in deliciously fragrant gardenia, and night-blooming jasmine.

Title: LA Original Candles
Body (HTML):
In collaboration with the Mayor's Fund of Los Angeles and the Mayor's Office of Economic Development, LA Original was developed to celebrate Los Angeles as the creative capital of the world.

Our exclusive LA Original candles feature three unique scents that celebrate the geographic diversity and beauty of this great city:

  • City Lights: Take your candle journey to the stage with this mosaic of patchouli, oak harvest tobacco, and wild flowers.
  • Canyon Sage: Experience the calming fragrance of desert cactus flowers and sage nestled in warm hints of citrus.
  • Coastal Breath: Tickle your nose with the essence of the salted ocean dew and soft floral hints of Jasmine.
  • Desert Bloom: This palette of wildflowers, lavender, and musk is reminiscent of your favorite desert day trip during a late spring super bloom.

Fresh new look coming soon

Title: LA LOVE Gift Set
Body (HTML):

From the city to the canyons, from the coast to the dessert, it's all love in LA.

As a show of support for our Angelino family, that has to stay safe at home for a couple more weeks, we’ve launched a special kit featuring our favorite LA Original candles, so you can bring the outside in!

In collaboration with the Mayor's Fund of Los Angeles and the Mayor's Office of Economic Development, LA Original was developed to celebrate Los Angeles as the creative capital of the world. Our exclusive LA Original candles feature four unique scents that celebrate the geographic diversity and beauty of this great city:

This gift set includes:
